      "message": "\u003e These are all device types that should\u0027ve been added to the top level\n\nI had taken Jagpal\u0027s resolution of your comment as actual resolution, so I do apologize for not giving you a longer time to come back.\n\nAre you just asking for a new \u0027ModbusPart\u0027 enum at a higher level that is referenced in the Type schema?  I\u0027m sure Jagpal would be amenable to fixing it up, or I can.",
